snippet.textDisplay: See how these Drs are dressed yeah take a good look now tell me is anyone else wearing full shields or eyewear when they go into a store? If the answer is No then what good is a mask over the mouth if we need all this outfit to stay safe? This means every last person will contract the dicease with or without a mask or the virus isnt as half as deadly and they want to instill fear in us.
